l:dependency.name: WebSphere Deployer Plugin
l:dependency.l:description: A Jenkins plugin for automatically deploying artifacts to a variety of WebSphere servers. Deploys your web artifacts locally or remotely to IBM WebSphere Application Server or IBM WebSphere Liberty Profile

l:dependency.name: Commons Lang
l:dependency.l:description: Commons Lang, a package of Java utility classes for the classes that are in java.lang's hierarchy, or are considered to be so standard as to justify existence in java.lang.
